%2F107203327_3189948617730378_3657068594769138935_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DZYvNrJAAMCsAX8tkXfi%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Ddc73d25a44c4cafc3f7cc18fdd627563%26oe%3D5F2F2B61&h=d35c6b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【民主派35+公民投票 (初選)】<br />\n[#請廣傳 : #更改公民投票驗證模式！]<br />\n<br />\n初選協調人收到法律意見，使用選民自行提供從選舉事務處網站查證選民記錄的截圖，有可能違反：第 541A 章 《選舉管理委員會(選民登記)(立法會地方選區)(區議會選區)規例》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因此，#民主動力 決定<strong><span class=\"red\">擱置使用任何選民驗證方法，包括網上查閱或截圖</span></strong>。現建議市民，進入服務站時，除展示身份證外，只需攜帶：<br />\n<br />\n✅ 過往的投票通知書 或<br />\n<br />\n✅ 住址證明 (文本、電子版本、截圖 及相片皆接納)，包括以下任何一種 :<br />\n<br />\n▶ (A) 符合運輸署規定可接受的住址證明 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/&hellip;/licence&hellip;/proof_of_address/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2Flicence%E2%80%A6%2Fproof_of_address%2Findex.html&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=4af94d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/&hellip;/licence&hellip;/proof_of_address/index.html</a><br />\n1. 水∕電∕煤∕中央石油氣供應商(不包括中央石油氣營運商)收費單或發票 ;<br />\n2. 固網電話∕流動電話∕收費電視∕互聯網收費單 ;<br />\n3. 銀行、持牌放債人、保險公司或強積金核准受託公司發出之結單或通知書 ;<br />\n4. 政府部門或司法機構(法庭)發出之文件 ;<br />\n例如:繳稅通知書、徵收差餉及∕或地租通知書、償還學生貸款通知書 ;<br />\n5. 本地大學或可頒授學位的高等教育院校發出的文件或收費單 ;<br />\n6. 由稅務局加蓋釐印的有效租約 ;<br />\n7. 下列公營機構發出的收費單、通知書或其他文件 :<br />\n&bull; 醫院管理局<br />\n&bull; 香港房屋委員會<br />\n&bull; 香港房屋協會<br />\n&bull; 香港考試及評核局<br />\n8. 下列機構發出的收費單、通知書或其他文件 :<br />\n&bull; 快易通(Autotoll)<br />\n&bull; 在港供應車輛用汽油∕柴油∕石油氣公司<br />\n&bull; 指定駕駛學校(包括:香港駕駛學院及觀塘駕駛學院)<br />\n&bull; 國際慈善機構(例如:聯合國兒童基金會)<br />\n&bull; 本地註冊的慈善機構(例如:香港公益金)<br />\n9. 有全名的屋苑住戶證 ;<br />\n10. 有屋苑或屋村全名的居民協會會員證 ;<br />\n或<br />\n▶ (B) 區內屋苑的居民證 ;<br />\n▶ (C) 區內居民組織的會員證 (須註有屋邨或屋苑名稱)。<br />\n<br />\n民主動力 Power for Democracy<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PowerForDemocracy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPowerForDemocracy%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=b5496b2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PowerForDemocracy/</a>"},{"pid":"d10d7bde36ee43e2c02dd647a132a55fcce1eb21","tid":2102020,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcfbe99d049dd110e466946f3e5860e74ef51cd","tid":2102020,"uid":305292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:17:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c008b1f16e17462ee855144805ad22ab2cdf4ce","tid":2102020,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9082f6a0eab4b65ee274e7cae8aa4259438a4bc9","tid":2102020,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d648d80bef5e0707cae430c99b9cd2cb37cb90fe","tid":2102020,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5adf4f332a6da725191ad545ec71000a3b5b206","tid":2102020,"uid":362431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"王伯當年係allinHK，咁算唔算有梁天琦認證？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />桐叔咁做怕唔怕俾民主黨屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"桐叔怕閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7924dd6208db28727c4a4aab59c2d62418ff7a61","tid":2102020,"uid":30907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:21:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"696a648e932c0c857b0a316aa51a408363353b34","tid":2102020,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:33:48.000Z","msg":"九東無既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b66e50e818998966eb93ebf223a667a6d6db43","tid":2102020,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=